An interesting post from China Hush on the problems caused by [Chinese mitten
crabs in German rivers](http://www.chinahush.com/2012/09/06/chinese-mitten-
crabs-invade-german-waters). To tackle the problem, German fishermen are
selling the crabs to Chinese restaurants.

